Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.55,0:00:06.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,结果 可能是太过于喜欢自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.78,0:00:13.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也讨厌被定性的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.50,0:00:18.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,个性之类的 也没人需要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:24.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没人需要就没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.69,0:00:26.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没有理由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.85,0:00:30.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被人需要什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.21,0:00:32.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很愉悦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.02,0:00:34.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,皆川同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.06,0:00:36.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,皆川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.95,0:00:39.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,皆川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.78,0:00:41.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你掉了东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.05,0:00:43.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,以前就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:48.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他是当时我的朋友暗恋的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:53.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾觉得他们真相衬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.73,0:00:57.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.84,0:01:01.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,同时 那应当出现的协调感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.19,0:01:05.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,却非常不融洽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.65,0:01:10.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 发了下呆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.72,0:01:16.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是对齐藤同学有些什么兴趣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.53,0:01:21.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可能只是对「齐藤同学对我的好意」有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.96,0:01:24.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,于是就手滑试了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.71,0:01:26.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.59,0:01:38.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊 刚才逃开了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.83,0:01:41.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只是吃了一惊而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:44.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两人真是很相衬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:49.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 完全 没有关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:52.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今后也要做好朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.12,0:01:56.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那一刻 我身体里涌现出来的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:58.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是罪恶感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.75,0:02:02.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也并非是肤浅的优越感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:08.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算死也不要像这样成为
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:10.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,「被榨取的一方」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.06,0:02:17.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起来从那天起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.72,0:02:20.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,觉醒了「榨取的快感」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.29,0:02:23.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很好吗 稍微像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.05,0:02:25.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.30,0:02:29.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢上自己以外的别人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:32.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不可能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.86,0:02:33.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,茜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.02,0:02:35.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,茜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:37.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,醒着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:39.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 寺内君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:42.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,之前和你交往的那个女朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:44.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？早就分手了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:48.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么吃醋了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:52.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 没有人能证明这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:56.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是个「有魅力的人」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.35,0:03:00.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,呐呐 起来了不那啥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:06.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明天还要早起了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.16,0:03:16.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉 没热情了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:24.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是没有人说「好」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:26.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就不知道有多好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:31.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 又在看着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.49,0:03:35.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真有这么喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:37.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对钟井老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:41.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个 皆川老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:47.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,放学后 你有时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:50.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…就一会儿 行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:55.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喝杯茶 聊下天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.41,0:03:58.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:01.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.08,0:04:05.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还剩下些不得不做的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:07.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那改天…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:08.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.00,0:04:12.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,放学后在音乐室里聊聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:15.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 不是今天的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:19.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:21.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:29.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你会过来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:34.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安乐冈 花火同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,---------------op -----------------
