Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭宋_GBK\fs75\pos(975,693)\fad(0,1100)}什么都没做不是吗。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:59.89,Kuzu_scene1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\fs90\fad(900,900)\c&H4B4B4B&\pos(1064,404.667)}三个月前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:12.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天一起的那个人是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:14.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老师的男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:19.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶嘿嘿 讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:22.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:27.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,…的话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:28.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安乐冈同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:31.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安乐冈花火同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:46.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是仅仅在无意中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:48.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,变成我这样的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:00.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,无意中？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:04.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 只是装作没有发觉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:12.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你如此地毫无防备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:14.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很吸引人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:18.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你最喜欢的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:20.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,钟井老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:23.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…哦…皆川老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:28.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你好 安乐冈同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:31.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的不可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:34.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,请…请问有何贵干
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:35.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.75,0:07:36.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也并不是特别地觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:41.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,钟井老师什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的菜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:38.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:41.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}你有东西忘在办公室了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:42.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}给 文件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:45.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}十…十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:49.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:53.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是想看到你受伤的表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:02.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以更多地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.87,0:08:06.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,更多更多地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:09.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看多点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:11.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:16.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:21.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安乐冈同学 放学后继续 在音乐教室里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:25.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:27.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好想快点看到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:30.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,「被榨取的你」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:35.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,…的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:47.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢自己还是讨厌自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:50.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,自身并没有如此强烈的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:52.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要说的话就是普通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:54.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得很无趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:56.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,像我这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:00.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在世时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:04.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是最高兴看见我成为教师的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:06.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已经早就不在人世
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:10.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,随年岁日渐淡忘的记忆中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:12.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩那长发
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:14.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能让我清晰地想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:19.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对 不错 正是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在春天里 对某人一见钟情什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:41.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我还真是单纯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:45.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哈 樱花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.36,0:09:49.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天早上也见过面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.59,0:09:50.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:53.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像你没发现呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:57.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才典礼的时候也有见到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:10:01.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天起我们都是新人了 请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:03.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这也太过于凑巧了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:05.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,正因太凑巧了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:08.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 你的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:10.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫皆川茜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:15.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这就是命运
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:22.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,钟井老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:24.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,迟到了真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.97,0:10:30.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:31.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:38.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要说的话 是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:45.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊算了 全部 一切所有都说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:46.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,轻松点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:49.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,总比没说出来就完结的好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.22,0:10:52.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:53.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:56.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:28.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,眼泪流不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:31.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 这不是理所当然的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:33.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我没有哭的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:35.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.75,0:11:41.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:42.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,努力过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.44,0:11:45.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会交往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:47.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真讨厌呐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:51.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,之后每天都要看到这幅景象
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.97,0:11:54.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这样 明明都明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:57.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然明白 虽然事已至此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:58.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不想听见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:02.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,反正即使在等待着也终有一天会知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:05.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么为什么不说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:08.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明一直都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:11.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为一直都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:12.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:15.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:20.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕 他不再是我的哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:23.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:26.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为这样才会被抢走的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.55,0:12:37.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦知道的话肯定也会感到痛苦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.10,0:12:39.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过总是会知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:45.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:49.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在只是想依赖麦而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:51.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不能因为我自己的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:55.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就成为可以去伤害麦的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.99,0:13:00.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,至今为止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:02.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是多么任性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:06.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天不去粟屋那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:12.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小 小绘…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:19.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,尾 尾随我来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:27.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 尾随你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:29.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:31.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.99,0:13:35.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会这么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:39.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,会这么喜欢像我这样的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.48,0:13:47.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:49.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:50.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:54.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个到底蕴含了多少意义
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:56.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:00.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:04.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:06.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:10.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不明白也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:14.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的 怎么可能没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:16.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:23.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,却无法停下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.94,0:14:28.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:32.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得我很可怜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:40.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:42.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不求更多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:44.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.81,0:14:45.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:48.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就看不到你的脸了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:50.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:52.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都看不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:14:59.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:05.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明直到刚才都没有迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:08.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对 直到刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明什么都没有的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.04,0:15:14.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,会心跳加速吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:15.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:18.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,会的吧 这么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.68,0:15:20.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.97,0:15:22.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我是女生？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:24.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:29.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为小绘是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.63,0:15:41.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,会和朋友做这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.59,0:15:44.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和粟屋也做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:51.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 花火
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:53.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快要哭了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:54.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,惹哭她了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:58.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌的话就说讨厌吧 呐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:01.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:03.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:06.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.58,0:16:08.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢小绘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:12.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.01,0:16:14.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是作为朋友的喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:19.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白我对花火而言是特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:23.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你不想失去我 无法拒绝我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.13,0:16:26.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就要趁虚而入了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.49,0:16:30.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你对我那么狠心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:34.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果注定得不到你的心意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:36.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,即使只是你的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:38.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想得到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:41.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好好地把我当成替代品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:44.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:49.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:53.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对他说了的话 他会是怎样的表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:57.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直一直都喜欢着你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:00.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.06,0:17:02.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 又开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:03.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,其实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.91,0:17:07.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,又是无法做到的妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:08.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不存在的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:15.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:19.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴唇好软
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.07,0:17:21.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有甜甜的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:24.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这样不行 因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:29.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么她是我认识的女生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:31.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:34.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:38.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火 告诉我你想怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:39.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,自己说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:42.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:45.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:47.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个就不做了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:51.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不说的话停下也行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.31,0:17:57.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对舒服的事情没辙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:17:59.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:02.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被小绘碰触的话有种…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:05.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有种很舒服的 感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.74,0:18:07.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:11.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:16.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我喜欢花火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:19.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是在触碰喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:21.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,会传达这样的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:23.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才会觉得舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.28,0:18:26.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:30.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,利用我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:32.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,来填满你的所有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:39.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人能给予的温暖是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:43.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事我明明不可能不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.33,0:18:53.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我却还是让小绘完全满足我的需求
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.27,0:19:02.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在更为寒冷的地方 独自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:08.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已经无法和小绘变回朋友了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:12.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:14.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你注意到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.37,0:19:19.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天第一次利用了别人的好感
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.58,0:19:23.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和抢走哥哥的那个女人一模一样的人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:24.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:31.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事 我当然明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:36.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我不是那个女人的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:40.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙早就察觉到了我的心思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:44.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且有意要践踏我的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:46.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉得到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:49.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,痛彻心扉一般 从头浇到脚的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.03,0:19:52.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,作为女人的…优越感
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:20:00.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,既然「现在」的我绝对赢不了她的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:06.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就要改变自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:08.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不管变成什么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.81,0:20:27.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 在生谁的气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:29.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,粟屋？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:30.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,钟井老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:36.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然你也察觉到了麦的心意了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.29,0:20:41.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:45.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为无法跟憧憬的人交往
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:48.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就找个近前的同级生交往算了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:50.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:54.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜那两个人喜欢的都是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.13,0:20:57.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被你不喜欢的男人喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:20:58.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,值得你那么高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.88,0:21:03.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.27,0:21:07.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明比从男人那里得到的好感
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.59,0:21:14.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,更令人愉悦的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.22,0:21:17.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:33.57,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}让我们一起逃离太阳系 在平行线相遇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:48.63,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}如同你我的影子般延伸着 平行线
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:55.10,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}将胆小怯懦归咎于时代的错也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:59.47,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}无处可归的我 找寻着愿望的归所
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:09.35,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}只愿成为你唇边溢出的只言片语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.21,0:22:19.82,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}让我们一起逃离太阳系 在平行线相遇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:30.01,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}带上无法实现的希冀 以及毫无底气的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.11,0:22:39.58,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}倘若感情全部流失殆尽 便由我开始描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.24,0:22:50.45,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}如今向你我的影子伸出手 平行线
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:33.57,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}太陽系を抜け出して　平行線で交わろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:48.63,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}私と君の影のように伸びている　あぁ平行線
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:55.10,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}勇気がないのは時代のせいにしてしまえばいい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:59.47,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}何処にも行けない　願いの居場所を探してた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:09.35,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}君の唇から　こぼれだす　言葉になりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.21,0:22:19.82,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}太陽系を抜け出して　平行線で交わろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:30.01,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}そんな叶わない望みも　不甲斐ない声も引き連れて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.11,0:22:39.58,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}感情全部流しきったら　描き始めてみせるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.24,0:22:50.45,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}私と君の影に今手を伸ばす　あぁ平行線
